{"tid":1603043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣新方向]痴爆紅綠燈 街坊都做得到","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T13:23:27.000Z","uid":42081,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2232da84f84a72bf1e37522363c218bf0277a1","tid":1603043,"uid":42081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">後日</span>都已經10月1 不如<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日</span>930痴10月1嘅文宣可以加痴喺屋企/翻工翻學附近<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">紅綠燈柱</span></span>? <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反正第日都10月1 摵左都唔心痛 重點要落中共面姐</span></strong><br />\n好處係<span style=\"color: red;\">人人都做得到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每人print少少 出門前貼定雙面膠紙 見到空嘅燈柱就<span style=\"color: orange;\">一野撻上去</span><br />\n<br />\n唔洗痴得好實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總之路過一野撻上去就得 <br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">最緊要煲得夠大 痴爆哂全港燈柱 所有人路過都要睇到</span><br />\n<br />\n最好喺<span style=\"color: gold;\">翻工/放工時間</span>前快閃去痴 一來快閃安全啲 二來人流多啲咁會多啲人望到 <br />\n<br />\n內容可以係:<br />\n 1. 10月1全民黑衫/國殤(遍唔遍地開花就自便啦)<br />\n 2. 10月1至7 三罷<br />\n 3. (黃藍鋪)有時間再貼啦<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4JwSvNL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4JwSvNL.jpg&h=42ada14c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qu0sjF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqu0sjF6.jpg&h=de039f44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZPkEF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZPkEF6.jpg&h=d2ef09e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TaCN37N.jpg\" data-thu